== 評價 ==
電影收穫了普遍影評人的差評。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的85篇專業影評文章，其中9篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為11%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]3.7分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1077027-batman_and_robin/ | title = Batman & Robin | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archive-date = 2015-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151024010314/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1077027-batman_and_robin/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的21篇評論文章，其中1篇予以好評，9篇差評，11篇褒貶不一，平均分為28（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-robin | title = Batman & Robin (1997): Reviews | work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher = [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate = 2010-04-17 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106002104/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-robin | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 票房 ==
《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》於1997年6月20日在北美發行，首映週末共收穫$42,872,605美元<ref name="box" />，為1997年電影中第三高的首週票房<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=1997&p=.htm| title= 1997 Domestic Grosses| work= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]| publisher= [[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]| accessdate= 2008-11-12| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20081216052510/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=1997&p=.htm| archivedate= 2008-12-16| deadurl= no}}</ref>，不過隔週便下滑了63%<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1116677093 | title = 'Bat' beats up B.O. | work = Variety | date = 1997-07-08 | accessdate = 2008-11-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606005907/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1116677093 | archivedate = 2011-06-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。最終，電影在北美的總票房為1.073億美元，其他地區1.309億美元，全球總計2.382億美元<ref name=box>{{cite web| url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=batmanrobin.htm| title= Batman and Robin| work= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]| publisher= Amazon.com| accessdate= 2008-11-12| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20081216120338/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=batmanrobin.htm| archivedate= 2008-12-16| deadurl= no}}</ref>。華納兄弟承認《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》在國內市場的失敗，但指出海外票房的成功<ref name="market" />。

